data.description: Welcome to this better-than-new home, built in 2019 and located right where you need to be! This cozy yet spacious house offers a smart layout with three separate sleeping areas, making it ideal for families or guests. Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan that's great for gatherings and everyday living. With a convenient cabana bath, entertaining becomes a breeze, especially when you're thinking of adding a pool to the backyard! The primary suite is your own oasis, complete with a relaxing soaking tub and TWO walk-in closets! Located centrally, you're just minutes away from everything you could want - shopping, dining, entertainment, highways and more! Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a home that's both practical and comfortable!
